data.description: No Lottery! First Come First Serve starting 11-21-2023. 1 bedroom Below Market Rate (BMR) housing opportunity available at 80% Area Median Income (AMI). Maximum income for 1 person = $80,700; 2 = $92,250; 3 = $103,750, etc. Must be 1st-time homebuyer & income eligible. Unit available thru the Mayor's Office of Housing and Community Development (MOHCD) & subject to resale controls, monitoring & other restrictions. Go to the SF Housing Portal (https://housing.sfgov.org)for First Come First Serve applications. Visit https://housing.sfgov.org for application & program info. Fair Housing Opportunity.
